{"tid":172462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"< 戴耀廷 > 表示  將投票予  曾俊華","createTime":"2017-03-26T02:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T02:37:18.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21bda8514dbea85e6ab337afddbe40529cd5413e","tid":172462,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】高等教育界選委戴耀廷表示，他和所有高教界選委均會投票予曾俊華，預計曾俊華可以得三百多票。他指自己是根據民間投票的結果投票，又指選舉策略不能只考慮政綱原則。<br />\n<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥表示，投票意向與經民聯一致，沒有回應是否投票給林鄭月娥。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=215461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215461&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c689f00a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215461&h=cdeb69dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=215461</a>"},{"pid":"a1dcf480017d2327e3246c2dbce9af2d3173ab54","tid":172462,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2014/09/1409241818472147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F09%2F1409241818472147.jpg&h=07541d92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"239b9a1dd2f17b0a74b40d7fa982edaa27d1a894","tid":172462,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:31:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d76377ff8e82b8cb0f8c216fc0bfb6bf33651028","tid":172462,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:34:54.000Z","msg":"佔中雨革係反831<br />\n<br />\n再投返比支持831嘅人<br />\n<br />\n去匡智會教書啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9bc015d8806fdfef2b45487406147099dff20a3","tid":172462,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\